dungeonette.data

Class RoomNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • dungeonette.data.RoomNode

  • public class RoomNode
extends java.lang.Object
    RoomNode is an RoomQueue'able container holding a single room object. A RoomNode knows both it's parent and it's child RoomNode.
